data.description: 10.29 Acres in the Roopville area of South Carroll County. Privacy at it's best! Land with beautiful Gum Creek along the backside of the property line. This home has a "Big" country front porch; a basement with finished space & a 2 car garage. Owner's suite is on the main level and extra large bedrooms upstairs with a nice Jack & Jill bathroom. Two HVAC units less than 3 yrs old; leaf guard gutters; a rear covered porch to enjoy morning sunrises and a new open deck to enjoy the outdoors. Entertain in the summer months with an inground pool (new liner installed this year). There are pet pens and a fenced garden spot. This home checks all the boxes!
